ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent Oxytocin medications.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) category related to Medication. The intent of this data element is to identify Oxytocin medications.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with RxNorm codes that identify medications that represent oxytocin as a single ingredient, administered in an injectable form.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that pertain to the drugs that have multiple ingredients. In addition, drugs with dose forms not consistent with injectable administration should not be included. The codes should be limited to those which are for human use and which are able to be prescribed in the US)
